WEBVTT

00:00.234 --> 00:01.750
Previously on Greenleaf.

00:01.851 --> 00:03.053
You preaching on Sunday?

00:03.154 --> 00:04.854
I don't preach anymore.

00:04.955 --> 00:06.489
You are Grace Greenleaf, ain't you?

00:06.590 --> 00:08.092
Daddy.

00:08.117 --> 00:10.226
Promise me you're not
here to sow discord.

00:10.327 --> 00:13.430
Because Jesus wants to welcome you home!

00:14.178 --> 00:16.599
Now he's the senior senator
from Tennessee.

00:16.700 --> 00:20.437
I think he's coming to ask me about
David Nelson, that trigger-happy cop,

00:20.538 --> 00:22.005
but I've never even met the man.

00:22.106 --> 00:23.373
The Senate is launching an inquiry

00:23.474 --> 00:25.075
into whether your church
and others like it

00:25.176 --> 00:27.377
are taking advantage
of your tax-exempt status.

00:27.478 --> 00:29.079
You better tell that little side piece

00:29.180 --> 00:31.581
to stop texting so damn much.

00:31.682 --> 00:33.016
You didn't lose my sister, Mama.

00:33.117 --> 00:35.285
You gave her away!

00:35.386 --> 00:36.653
One of the cops who works around here

00:36.754 --> 00:39.355
told me about a 15-year-old girl

00:39.457 --> 00:41.724
- from the church.
- He did it again?

00:41.826 --> 00:43.560
Just like Faith.

00:43.661 --> 00:45.395
I don't think he ever really stopped.

00:52.136 --> 00:53.603
So, what's in here?

00:53.704 --> 00:55.805
Girl's name, phone number,

00:55.906 --> 00:58.308
address, statements...

00:58.409 --> 00:59.709
the ones she made the first time

00:59.810 --> 01:01.311
and when she recanted.

01:01.950 --> 01:03.713
He just gave this to you?

01:03.814 --> 01:07.584
He is a she, and she gets it.

01:09.920 --> 01:12.571
Your Uncle Mac raped this child.

01:14.024 --> 01:16.326
Now, Gigi, God's giving
you a second chance.

01:16.983 --> 01:18.383
Take it.

